## Summary
This documentation covers the installation and configuration of Session Replay for iOS applications using either the iOS Swift SDK or legacy iOS SDK, explaining how the plugin captures view tree changes to create video-like replays, with options for sampling rate, data masking, and integration methods via Swift Package Manager or CocoaPods.

